### Steps to Reproduce

1. Create a Navigation page in master detail page and initial the Detail property in constructor with it
2. Push a page in navigation at master detail page constructor.
3. Pop the pages by back button until it reaches to root page.

### Expected Behavior
Pop the pages to root page
### Actual Behavior
When pop the pages until reaches to root, it throws this exception : 

